OL,5, A life insurance firm has defended     
OL,6, using serial killer Harold Shipman in  
OL,7, an advertising campaign after it was   
OL,8, labelled "beyond despicable" by other  
OL,9, industry leaders.                      
OL,11,FDeadHappy used the image to promote its
OL,12,Fservices with the tagline "Life        
OL,13,FInsurance. Because you never know who  
OL,14,Fyour doctor might be."                 
OL,16,FThe firm said it was meant to "make    
OL,17,Fpeople stop and think".                
OL,19,FThe brand intended to be provocative   
OL,20,Fbut not to offend people, it added.    
